  "description": "<p>✔ Up to $7500 + $900 Car Allow + Bonuses + Comms + Good Benefits</p><p>✔ Valve, Gauges & Fitting MNC</p><p>✔ West SG<br /></p><p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong><br /></p><p>• Develop new sales accounts in the Semiconductor Industry</p><p>• Maintain customer relationships, and own the end-to-end sales process and customer journey</p><p>• Plan and implement strategies, reporting accurately on sales and business activities</p><p>• Update market and industry trends on weekly basis</p><p>• Perform any other ad-hoc duties as assigned<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br /></p><p>• Minimum 5-7 years of relevant <strong>Sales </strong>Experience in the Semiconductor Industry with track records in <strong>selling fluid components</strong><br /></p><p><strong>*Interested applicants, please send your resume with reason(s) for leaving previous employment(s), notice period, last drawn and expected salary to josephyap[at]recruitfirst.com.sg</strong><br /></p><p><strong>All applications will be treated with strictest confidentiality. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Thank you.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>RecruitFirst Pte Ltd E.A. 13C6342</strong></p><p><strong>Joseph Yap Shi Hao (R1767577)</strong> </p>",
